ggsunburst 0.0.2
================

new functionality:
  tile function to include a geom_tile (similar to a heatmap) layer

changes:
  sunburst and icicle do not accept the following arguments anymore: labels, text.size, text.color.
  sunburst and icicle now accept these arguments: leaf_labels, leaf_labels.size, leaf_labels.color, node_labels, node_labels.size, node_labels.color and	node_labels.min.
  sunbust_data$node_labels now have additional variables: rhjust, pvjust and delta_angle.
  bug fixes
  

ggsunburst 0.0.1
================

new functionality:
  sunburst_data accepts node_atributes parameter to include node attributes in its output

changes:
  bug fixes


ggsunburst 0.0
============

Experimental release of package.

Supports extraction of plot data for the following format:

* newick format (input as string or file)